high_descs: Turn left and move towards the refrigerator, then turn left and move to the table with the toaster on top.
Pick up the cup between the knife and the egg from the rear of the table.
Turn around and move to the refrigerator and then turn around to face the door of the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator, place the cup on the top shelf to the left of the lettuce, chill the cup, open the refrigerator, pick up the cup from the top shelf, then close the refrigerator.
Turn to the right, move past the sink to the table next to the oven, then turn towards the small table in between the garbage bag and the counter.
Place the cup on the front center of the table; to the right of the salt shaker and in front of the cup.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled cup on the table.

high_descs: Turn left, go to the refrigerator, turn left, go to the white table with the toaster on it.
Take the cup on the table closest to the wall.
Turn around, go to the refrigerator.
Put the cup to the right of the lettuce in the refrigerator. Close then open the refrigerator. Take the cup from the refrigerator.
Turn left, go to the black stand next to the end of the sink counter and a black trash bag.
Put the cup in front of and to the left of the cup on the stand.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold cup on a stand.

high_descs: Turn right and move across the room to the white table on the right.
Pick up the gray vase at the back of the table, closest to the wall.
Turn around and move to the refrigerator on the left.
Open the fridge and place the vase on the top shelf. close the door, wait a moment, and take the vase out of the fridge
Turn left and move across the room to the black three tiered table on the right.
Put the vase on the top shelf of the table in front and slightly left of the other vase.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled vase on the three tiered black table.
